Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Kennedy quits presidential bid
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx01
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Dec 1982
Edward Kennedy decides against running as Democrat candidate in the next presidential election. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less